<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1- ạllhu qad̊ kẖalãṣ̊tanā
 wadaʿ̊waẗaⁿ daʿaẘtanā
 biạl̊qaṣ̊di wālnĩʿ̊maẗi lạ
 biʿamaliⁿ yuʿ̊zay̱ lanā

[V2]
 2- fayā laʿuẓ̊mi niʿ̊maẗiⁿ
 qab̊la ạldũhūri ạủʿ̊ṭīat̊
 fī rabĩnā wahakadẖā
 bisẖakẖ̊ṣihi qad̊ ạủẓ̊hirat̊

[V3]
 3- yā ʿajabaⁿạ min̊ niʿ̊maẗiⁿ
 fī ạảm̊rihā ạl̊kulũ yaḥār̊
 laẙsa lahā bad̊ʾuⁿ walạ
 ḥadũ yuray̱ walạ qarār̊

[V4]
 4- kẖalạṣunā bihā ʿajīb̊
 ạảsāsuhu damu ạlṣãlīb̊
 fal̊nab̊tahij̊ fī kulĩ ḥīn̊
 bidẖalika ạl̊ḥubĩ ạl̊ʿajīb̊

[V5]
 5- fālsẖũk̊ra nuh̊dīka ʿalay̱
 kamāli dẖā ạl̊ḥubĩ ạlsãnī̃
 ḥubiⁿ̃ lanā ạảb̊daẙtahu
 fī ạlrãbĩ yasūʿa ạl̊gẖanī̃</lyrics>
<title>ạllh qd kẖlṣtnạ</title>
</song>